(3) All records and documents in the custody of the Surveyor-General shall become the property of the Government, but approved plans and diagrams shall be available, for the purposes of reference, to the public in the office of the Surveyor-General . [As amended by S.I. No. 65 of 1965 and No. 9 of 1973] [*27th August, 1965.]
